    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You must be in a Jyuuken stance to use this technique. You make 4 Jyuuken attacks against the target, at your highest attack bonus. These attacks cannot score a critical hit and deal only half damage, but each hit deals an additional 1 point of Chakra damage, as well as 16 tenketsu damage. A creature's Chakra Pool cannot be reduced below 1 due to this damage. The target is @Condition[dazed;duration=1]{dazed} for 1 round (Fortitude negates).<br><br>Each additional time this technique or Hyuuga Ryuu: Ougi - Hakke Hyakunijuuhachi Shou is used against the same creature within a 24 hour period reduces the tenketsu damage per hit by 4.</p>\n\n\n\n",
